He has travelled to more than 113 countries. He started his own YouTube Political channel, â€œNeutral by Javed Chaudhryâ€, Training & Coaching channel â€œMind changerâ€ and a Travel channel titled â€œTravel with Javed Chaudhryâ€. 

In recognition of his contributions, he was awarded the prestigious Sitara-e-Imtiaz. He was also awarded the honorary Doctorate of Philosophy degree by Islamia University, Bahawalpur in November 2023.
